Think of an aged Facebook profile as a head start. Instead of fighting the suspicion Meta places on brand-new accounts, you begin with years of genuine history already working in your favor.

### Why aged profiles win

Meta trusts accounts with a long, consistent track record, and that trust pays off directly in your campaigns:

1. **Lower disable rates**, your account is far less likely to be flagged.
2. **Greater stability**, campaigns run with fewer interruptions.
3. **Faster scaling**, established trust supports higher spend sooner.

### Choose your tier

| Tier | Profile age | Best for |
| --- | --- | --- |
| **Aged Profiles** | Established | Everyday campaigns and most advertisers |
| **Super Aged Profiles** | 7+ years | Large-scale campaigns and high spending |

At GOADS, we supply only the highest quality, most premium aged profiles, each hand-selected for the lowest disable rates and maximum stability.

{% callout variant="tip" title="Not sure which to pick?" %}
For day-to-day campaigns, an Aged Profile is plenty. When you need the strongest possible foundation for heavy spend, go Super Aged. Still unsure? [Ask our team](/docs/questions-bank/support) and we will match you to the right tier.
{% /callout %}
